GET /api/organizations/{org}/chat_conversations/{conv}?tree=True&rendering_mode=messages&render_all_tools=true&consistency=eventual returns the entire tree as a flat array of message nodes. Capture sizes range from ~10KB up to 11.7MB for long-running conversations — the response is unbounded and must be streamed/paginated client-side. Each node:

