§5 — Evidence Headers
Every forwarded response gets these headers. They are the wire-level proof that mutation occurred.

Header	Type	Set on
x-wc-system-stripped	true|false	always
x-wc-mutation-mode	mode name	always
x-wc-canary-injected	true|false	always
x-wc-canary-echoed	true|false	post-stream (trailer or KV-only)
x-wc-original-system-len	int	always
