Tampermonkey → Dashboard → "Create a new script" → paste the file above.
Tampermonkey → Dashboard → script settings → set WORKER_C_URL and WORKER_C_WS to the operator's Worker C deployment (or http://127.0.0.1:8787 for local Cloudflare dev / wrangler dev).
