Press Alt+Shift+B — diagnostics panel appears bottom-right.
Send a message in chat → intercept counter ticks; Worker C log shows the request.
The fact that the operator never copies a cookie value anywhere is the safety property: cookies stay in the browser, the userscript only ever requests credentials: 'include', and Worker C only ever sees the response — never the cookie.

