Constraint	Rationale
fetch('/api/bootstrap/{org}/current_user_access', {credentials:'include'}) is the only auth path	Browser auto-supplies cookies; the script never sees them
Response shape is the canonical one captured in HAR (account.uuid, organization.uuid, memberships[], permissions[])	Reused for Worker A's mock identity surface mimic
Setup-token gating on the POST to Worker C /bridge/session	Prevents arbitrary pages from POSTing to the operator's Worker C
Email is redacted before posting (local_part → first 2 chars + ***)	Even though the operator owns both endpoints, redaction is defense-in-depth
org_uuid discovery falls back to window.__NEXT_DATA__ and <meta> tags if /api/bootstrap is path-restricted	Robust against edge-cache routing changes
